<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Schenk Trockenbau Koblenz – Moderne Wand- und Deckengestaltung</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">
<meta name="description" content="Schenk Trockenbau Koblenz – Ihr Experte für Trockenbau, Deckengestaltung und Innenausbau seit 2011.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--blau:#01269E;--grau:#626262;--dunkel:#111;--hell:#f8f8f8;--weiss:#fff;--nav-h:88px;}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;color:var(--dunkel);background:var(--weiss);overflow-x:hidden;}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;height:var(--nav-h);background:white;box-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.08);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 5%;transition:box-shadow 0.3s;}
nav.scrolled{box-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);}
.nav-logo{text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.logo-wrap{display:inline-flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch;gap:1px;}
.logo-img{height:60px;width:auto;display:block;}
.logo-claim{font-size:12px;font-style:italic;color:#3a3a3a;letter-spacing:0.02em;text-align:right;}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center;}
.nav-links a{color:var(--dunkel);text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color 0.3s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--blau);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--dunkel)!important;color:white!important;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:2px;font-weight:600;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--blau)!important;}
.burger{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;cursor:pointer;}
.burger span{width:24px;height:2px;background:var(--dunkel);border-radius:2px;}
.mob-menu{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--blau);z-index:999;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:32px;}
.mob-menu.open{display:flex;}
.mob-menu a{color:white;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,5vw,44px);font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;}
.mob-close{position:fixed;top:24px;right:5%;color:white;font-size:32px;cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;}

/* HERO */
#hero{height:calc(100svh - var(--nav-h) - 52px);margin-top:var(--nav-h);position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:url("data:image/jpeg;base64,") center/cover no-repeat;}
#hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(120deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.25) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 60%);z-index:1;}
.hero-inner{position:absolute;inset:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;z-index:2;}
.hero-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:clamp(40px,5vw,70px) 5% clamp(40px,5vw,70px) clamp(40px,7%,100px);}
.hero-rechts{display:flex;align-self:flex-start;align-items:center;padding:clamp(30px,4vw,50px) 5% clamp(30px,4vw,50px) 0;max-height:calc(100svh - var(--nav-h) - 52px);transform:scale(0.65);opacity:0;animation:zoomInSmall 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94) 0.5s forwards;}
.hero-rechts img{width:100%;height:auto;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain;display:block;box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);}
.hero-tag{margin-bottom:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);letter-spacing:0.12em;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);animation:fromBottom 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 0.7s forwards;}
.hero-h1{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,5vw,6rem);font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.1;color:white;margin-bottom:20px;text-shadow:0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);animation:fromBottom 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 0.95s forwards;}
.hero-h1 em{font-style:normal;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-weight:300;}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.4vw,1.3rem);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:32px;max-width:420px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);animation:fromBottom 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.2s forwards;}
.hero-btn-wrap{opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);animation:fromBottom 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.45s forwards;}
.hero-btn{display:inline-block;background:white;color:var(--dunkel);padding:14px 32px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border-radius:2px;transition:all 0.3s;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);}
.hero-btn:hover{background:var(--blau);color:white;transform:translateY(-2px);}
@keyframes fromBottom{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
@keyframes zoomInSmall{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(0.65);}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}}
@keyframes fromLeft{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-40px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0);}}
@keyframes fromRight{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(80px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0);}}

/* TICKER */
.ticker-wrap{background:var(--blau);padding:16px 0;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;}
.ticker{display:inline-flex;animation:ticker 30s linear infinite;}
.ticker-item{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);padding:0 32px;}
.ticker-item span{color:white;}
@keyframes ticker{from{transform:translateX(0);}to{transform:translateX(-50%);}}

/* GALERIE */
#galerie{background:#0f0f0f;padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 0;}
.gal-header{text-align:center;padding:0 5%;margin-bottom:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);}
.gal-header h2{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,48px);font-weight:400;color:white;line-height:1.25;}
.gal-header h2 em{font-style:normal;display:block;}
.gal-slider-wrap{position:relative;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 5%;}
.gal-slider{position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:4px;}
.gal-slide{display:none;position:relative;cursor:pointer;}
.gal-slide.aktiv{display:block;}
.gal-slide img{width:100%;height:clamp(280px,48vw,520px);object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform 0.4s ease;}
.gal-slide:hover img{transform:scale(1.02);}
.gal-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 0%,transparent 55%);}
.gal-label{position:absolute;bottom:52px;left:28px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:white;letter-spacing:0.02em;text-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);}
.gal-click-hint{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:28px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:white;font-size:13px;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:0.04em;transition:background 0.3s;}
.gal-slide:hover .gal-click-hint{background:rgba(1,38,158,0.8);}
.gal-pfeile{position:absolute;right:-60px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
.gal-pfeil{width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);color:white;font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.3s;}
.gal-pfeil:hover{background:white;color:var(--dunkel);}
.gal-dots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-top:20px;}
.gal-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;}
.gal-dot.aktiv{background:white;transform:scale(1.3);}
.ref-liste{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 5%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;}
.ref-empty{text-align:center;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);padding:80px 20px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:0.05em;}
.ref-karte{background:#1a1a1a;border-radius:6px;padding:32px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:40% 1fr;gap:32px;align-items:start;}
.ref-titelbild-wrap{position:relative;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
.ref-titelbild{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;object-fit:cover;display:block;}
.ref-vorher-tag{position:absolute;top:12px;left:12px;background:var(--blau);color:white;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:2px;}
.ref-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.ref-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:white;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.02em;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:14px;}
.ref-text{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.78);line-height:1.7;}
.ref-galerie{grid-column:1/-1;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:8px;margin-top:8px;}
.ref-thumb{width:100%;aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;display:block;transition:transform 0.3s ease,opacity 0.3s ease;}
.ref-thumb:hover{transform:scale(1.04);opacity:0.85;}

/* LIGHTBOX */
.lb-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.92);z-index:2000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;}
.lb-overlay.open{display:flex;}
.lb-box{background:white;max-width:1100px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 380px;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
.lb-foto-wrap{position:relative;background:#111;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.lb-main-img{width:100%;height:clamp(300px,50vh,600px);object-fit:cover;display:block;}
.lb-thumbs{display:flex;gap:6px;padding:10px;background:#0a0a0a;overflow-x:auto;}
.lb-thumb{width:64px;height:48px;object-fit:cover;cursor:pointer;opacity:0.5;border:2px solid transparent;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0;transition:all 0.2s;}
.lb-thumb.aktiv,.lb-thumb:hover{opacity:1;border-color:var(--blau);}
.lb-vorher-tag{position:absolute;top:12px;left:12px;background:var(--blau);color:white;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:2px;}
.lb-info{padding:36px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow-y:auto;}
.lb-kat{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blau);margin-bottom:8px;}
.lb-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:var(--dunkel);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.1;}
.lb-text{font-size:15px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:24px;}
.lb-count{font-size:13px;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:auto;}
.lb-anfrage{display:inline-block;background:var(--blau);color:white;padding:13px 24px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border-radius:2px;margin-top:24px;text-align:center;transition:all 0.3s;}
.lb-anfrage:hover{background:#0133cc;}
.lb-close{position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);color:white;border:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:10;}
.lb-nav{position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);color:white;border:none;width:44px;height:44px;font-size:22px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:10;transition:background 0.3s;}
.lb-nav:hover{background:rgba(1,38,158,0.8);}
.lb-prev{left:10px;}
.lb-next{right:10px;}

/* LEISTUNGEN */
#leistungen-wrap{padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;background:var(--weiss);}
.leist-inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
.sek-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blau);margin-bottom:12px;}
.sek-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,50px);font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.02em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);}
.leist-grid{border-top:1px solid #e8e8e8;}
.leist-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 220px 1fr 88px;gap:32px;padding:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px) 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8;align-items:start;transition:all 0.3s ease;}
.leist-item:hover{background:var(--hell);}
.leist-item:hover{background:#f0f4ff;border-left:3px solid var(--blau);padding-left:17px;transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(1,38,158,0.1);}
.leist-item:hover .leist-nr{color:var(--blau);}
.leist-nr{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,2vw,26px);font-weight:700;color:var(--blau);line-height:1.3;}
.leist-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.2vw,26px);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.02em;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1.15;padding-top:4px;}
.leist-body p{font-size:15px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:12px;}
.leist-body ul{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px 18px;}
.leist-body li{font-size:13px;color:var(--dunkel);font-weight:700;}
.leist-body li::before{content:"● ";color:var(--blau);font-size:9px;}
.leist-icon{width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--blau);color:var(--blau);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.leist-icon svg{width:36px;height:36px;}
.leist-item:hover .leist-icon{background:var(--blau);color:white;border-color:var(--blau);}

/* ÜBER UNS */
#ueber{background:var(--hell);padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;}
.ueber-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
.ueber-aussage{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,46px);font-weight:400;line-height:1.3;color:var(--dunkel);max-width:820px;margin-bottom:clamp(40px,5vw,64px);}
.was-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(32px,5vw,80px);align-items:center;}
.ausmacht-punkte{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;}
.ausmacht-punkt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;background:white;padding:20px 24px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;transition:transform 0.3s ease,box-shadow 0.3s ease,border-color 0.3s,background 0.3s;}
.ausmacht-punkt:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(1,38,158,0.15);border-color:var(--blau);background:#f0f4ff;}
.ausmacht-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blau);color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ausmacht-text{font-size:15px;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1.5;font-weight:500;}
.ausmacht-foto{position:relative;}
.ausmacht-foto img{width:100%;border-radius:4px;object-fit:cover;height:clamp(280px,38vw,480px);display:block;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);}
.ausmacht-badge{position:absolute;bottom:24px;left:-16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);padding:18px 22px;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);max-width:230px;}
.badge-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--blau);color:white;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:10px;}
.ausmacht-badge p{font-size:13px;color:#01269E;line-height:1.5;font-weight:600;}

/* STATS */
.stats-bar{background:var(--blau);padding:clamp(28px,4vw,44px) 5%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:24px;text-align:center;}
.stat-zahl{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,50px);font-weight:600;color:white;}
.stat-label{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px;}

/* KONTAKT */
#kontakt{background:white;}

/* Teil 1: Info + Karte */
.kontakt-top{padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.2fr;gap:clamp(40px,6vw,80px);align-items:center;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;}
.kontakt-claim-h{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,52px);font-weight:500;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1.15;margin-top:12px;}
.kontakt-karte{background:#2d2d2d;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;}
.kontakt-foto-wrap{position:relative;}
.kontakt-foto{width:100%;height:260px;object-fit:cover;display:block;object-position:center bottom;}
.kontakt-foto-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent 50%,#2d2d2d 100%);}
.kontakt-foto-titel{position:absolute;bottom:16px;left:0;right:0;text-align:center;color:white;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.05em;}
.kontakt-daten{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px;padding:24px;}
.kontakt-daten-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:6px;}
.kontakt-daten-wert{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.5;}
.kontakt-daten-wert a{color:var(--blau);text-decoration:none;}
.kontakt-daten-wert a:hover{color:white;}

/* Teil 2: Formular */
.kontakt-form-section{background:#2d2d2d;padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;}
.kontakt-form-inner{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:20px;}
.kontakt-form-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,44px);font-weight:400;color:white;text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;}
.k-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;}
.form-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;}
.form-field label{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);letter-spacing:0.08em;}
.k-form input,.k-form textarea,.k-form select{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;padding:14px 18px;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-size:15px;border-radius:4px;outline:none;transition:border 0.3s;width:100%;}
.k-form input::placeholder,.k-form textarea::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);}
.k-form input:focus,.k-form textarea:focus{border-color:var(--blau);}
.k-form textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:150px;}
.kontakt-form-section .form-2col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
.k-form select option{background:#222;}
.form-check{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;}
.form-check input[type="checkbox"]{width:18px;height:18px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;accent-color:var(--blau);}
.form-check label{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);line-height:1.6;}
.form-check label a{color:var(--blau);}
.submit-btn{background:var(--blau);color:white;border:none;padding:16px 40px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;border-radius:4px;transition:all 0.3s;align-self:flex-start;}
.submit-btn:hover{background:#0133cc;transform:translateY(-2px);}

/* Teil 3: FAQ */
.faq-section{background:white;padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;}
.faq-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:280px 1fr;gap:clamp(40px,6vw,80px);align-items:start;}
.faq-score{margin-top:32px;}
.faq-score-nr{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dunkel);}
.faq-score-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--grau);margin-top:4px;}
.faq-titel{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,40px);font-weight:600;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:32px;}
.faq-titel span{color:var(--blau);}
.faq-liste{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8;}
.faq-frage{width:100%;background:none;border:none;padding:20px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--dunkel);cursor:pointer;text-align:left;gap:16px;transition:color 0.3s;}
.faq-frage:hover{color:var(--blau);}
.faq-frage.offen{color:var(--blau);}
.faq-pfeil{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.3s;color:var(--blau);}
.faq-frage.offen .faq-pfeil{transform:rotate(90deg);}
.faq-antwort{display:none;padding:0 0 20px 0;}
.faq-antwort.offen{display:block;}
.faq-antwort p{font-size:15px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.75;}


/* FOOTER */
footer{background:#0a0a0a;padding:26px 5%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;border-top:1px solid #1a1a1a;}
.footer-logo{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:white;text-decoration:none;}
.footer-links{display:flex;gap:22px;}
.footer-links a{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.3s;}
.footer-links a:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);}
.footer-copy{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-size:12px;}

/* REVEAL */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(36px);transition:opacity 0.8s ease,transform 0.8s ease;}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.reveal-up{opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease,transform 0.7s ease;}
.reveal-up.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.reveal-left{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-60px);transition:opacity 0.7s ease,transform 0.7s ease;}
.reveal-left.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0);}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:900px){
  /* NAV */
  .nav-links{display:none;}
  .burger{display:flex;}
  .logo-img{height:44px;}
  .logo-claim{font-size:10px;}
  /* HERO */
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-template-rows:1fr;}
  #hero{height:calc(100svh - var(--nav-h) - 52px);}
  .hero-links{padding:clamp(32px,8vw,60px) 6% clamp(32px,8vw,60px);justify-content:center;}
  .hero-h1{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,6vw,2.5rem);}
  .hero-sub{font-size:16px;max-width:100%;}
  .hero-rechts{display:none;}
  /* GALERIE */
  .gal-pfeile{display:none;}
  .gal-click-hint{font-size:12px;}
  .ref-karte{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:18px;padding:20px;}
  .ref-galerie{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:6px;}
  /* LEISTUNGEN */
  .leist-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:56px 1fr;grid-template-rows:auto auto;gap:4px 12px;padding:20px 12px;align-items:start;}
  .leist-nr{font-size:20px;line-height:1.3;grid-column:1;grid-row:1;}
  .leist-titel{font-size:17px;grid-column:2;grid-row:1;padding-top:6px;}
  .leist-body{grid-column:1/-1;grid-row:2;}
  .leist-icon{display:none;}
  .leist-body p{font-size:14px;max-width:100%;}
  .leist-body ul{gap:4px 12px;}
  .leist-body li{font-size:13px;}
  #leistungen-wrap{padding:40px 5%;}
  /* PROZESS */
  .prozess-carousel-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;overflow:hidden;}
  .prozess-vp{width:100%;overflow:hidden;}
  .prozess-track{display:flex;gap:0;transition:transform 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);}
  .prozess-karte{flex:0 0 100%;width:100%;min-width:0;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;}
  .prozess-arr{display:none;}
  .prozess-pfeil{display:none;}
  .prozess-dots-mobile{display:flex;}
  /* Prozess karte mobile layout */
  .prozess-karte .prozess-icon{display:none;}
  .prozess-karte .prozess-nr{display:inline-block;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .prozess-karte h3{font-size:17px;}
  /* BEWERTUNGEN */
  .bew-karte{flex:0 0 80vw;height:auto;}
  .bew-arrow{display:none;}
  .bew-gesamt{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;}
  /* ÜBER UNS */
  .was-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .ausmacht-badge{left:0;bottom:12px;max-width:200px;}
  .ueber-aussage{font-size:clamp(20px,5vw,32px);}
  /* STATS */
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;padding:32px 5%;}
  .stat-zahl{font-size:clamp(28px,7vw,44px);}
  /* KONTAKT */
  .kontakt-top{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:40px 5%;}
  .kontakt-daten{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:16px;}
  .kontakt-form-section{clip-path:none;padding:40px 5%;}
  .form-2col{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .kontakt-form-titel{font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,32px);}
  /* FAQ */
  .faq-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .faq-score{margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:32px;}
  /* LIGHTBOX */
  .lb-overlay{padding:0 !important;align-items:flex-end !important;}
  .lb-box{display:flex !important;flex-direction:column !important;grid-template-columns:none !important;max-height:92vh;width:100% !important;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;overflow-y:auto;}
  .lb-foto-wrap{width:100%;position:relative;}
  .lb-main-img{width:100% !important;height:auto !important;max-height:55vh;object-fit:contain !important;background:#111;}
  .lb-info{padding:16px;overflow-y:auto;max-height:40vh;}
  .lb-thumbs{display:flex;gap:6px;padding:8px;overflow-x:auto;}
  .lb-thumb{width:52px;height:40px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .lb-nav{top:40%;}
  .lb-close{top:8px;right:8px;}
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
  footer{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;}
  .footer-links{flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;}
  .gal-label{font-size:18px;bottom:40px;left:16px;}
  .gal-click-hint{left:16px;bottom:12px;}
  .kontakt-karte{border-radius:8px;}
  .captcha-box{max-width:100%;}
  .bew-karte{flex:0 0 88vw;}
}
@media (min-width:768px) and (max-width:1100px),
       (min-width:600px) and (max-width:1366px) and (orientation:portrait),
       (min-width:1100px) and (max-width:2000px) and (orientation:portrait){
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-template-rows:auto 1fr;}
  .hero-links{padding:clamp(40px,5vw,70px) 6% clamp(20px,3vw,40px);justify-content:flex-start;}
  .hero-h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem);}
  .hero-sub{font-size:15px;max-width:600px;}
  .hero-rechts{display:flex;align-self:start;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;max-width:85%;margin:2rem auto 0;padding:0 0 clamp(30px,5vw,50px);max-height:none;transform:translateX(80px);animation:fromRight 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94) 0.5s forwards;}
  .hero-rechts img{width:auto;max-width:100%;max-height:42vh;height:auto;object-fit:contain;}
  .hero-tag{transform:translateX(-40px);animation:fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 0.7s forwards;}
  .hero-h1{transform:translateX(-40px);animation:fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 0.95s forwards;}
  .hero-sub{transform:translateX(-40px);animation:fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.2s forwards;}
  .hero-btn-wrap{transform:translateX(-40px);animation:fromLeft 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.45s forwards;}
}
@media (min-width:1000px) and (max-width:1366px) and (orientation:landscape){
  .hero-links{padding-bottom:180px;}
  .hero-h1{font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3.5vw,2.5rem);}
  .hero-sub{font-size:14px;}
  .hero-btn-wrap{margin-top:1rem;}
  .hero-rechts{align-self:flex-start;max-height:60vh;overflow:hidden;}
  .hero-rechts img{height:auto;max-height:55vh;width:auto;object-fit:contain;display:block;}
}
/* PROZESS */
#prozess{padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;background:var(--hell);}
.prozess-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
.prozess-header{margin-bottom:clamp(40px,5vw,60px);}
.prozess-sub{font-size:16px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.7;margin-top:14px;max-width:600px;}
@media(min-width:901px){
  .prozess-track{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;gap:0;align-items:stretch;margin-bottom:48px;}
  .prozess-arr{display:none;}
  .prozess-pfeil{font-size:32px;color:#ccc;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:0 8px;}
}
.prozess-karte{background:white;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;border-radius:8px;padding:28px 24px;transition:box-shadow 0.3s,transform 0.3s;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.prozess-karte p{font-size:14px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.65;}
.prozess-karte:hover{box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(1,38,158,0.1);transform:translateY(-4px);}
.prozess-nr{display:inline-block;background:var(--blau);color:white;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:16px;align-self:flex-start;}
.prozess-icon{width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:#f0f4ff;color:var(--blau);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:8px 0 16px;}
.prozess-icon svg{width:28px;height:28px;}
.prozess-karte h3{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--dunkel);}
.prozess-karte p{font-size:14px;color:var(--grau);line-height:1.65;}
.prozess-cta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.prozess-tel{font-size:16px;color:var(--dunkel);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;}
.prozess-tel:hover{color:var(--blau);}

/* BEWERTUNGEN */
#bewertungen{padding:clamp(60px,8vw,100px) 5%;background:white;}
.bew-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;}
.bew-header{margin-bottom:clamp(36px,5vw,52px);}
.bew-carousel-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.bew-viewport{overflow:hidden;width:100%;}
.bew-track{display:flex;gap:16px;transition:transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);}
.bew-karte{background:var(--hell);border:1px solid #e8e8e8;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;height:240px;flex:0 0 calc(33.333% - 11px);box-sizing:border-box;transition:box-shadow 0.3s;}
.bew-karte:hover{box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);}
.bew-top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
.bew-sterne{color:#fbbc04;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px;}
.bew-text-wrap{flex:1;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.bew-text{font-size:13px;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1.6;font-style:italic;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:4;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden;margin:0;}
.bew-text.expanded{display:block;-webkit-line-clamp:unset;overflow:visible;}
.bew-mehr{display:none;background:none;border:none;color:var(--blau);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;padding:0;text-decoration:underline;margin-top:4px;}
.bew-mehr.show{display:inline-block;}
.bew-autor{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0;}
.bew-avatar{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blau);color:white;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.bew-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dunkel);}
.bew-quelle{font-size:11px;color:var(--grau);}
.bew-arrow{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:white;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:all 0.3s;color:var(--dunkel);}
.bew-arrow:hover{background:var(--blau);color:white;border-color:var(--blau);}
.bew-dots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:36px;}
.bew-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#e0e0e0;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;border:none;}
.bew-dot.aktiv{background:var(--blau);transform:scale(1.3);}
.bew-gesamt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.bew-score{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.bew-score-nr{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dunkel);line-height:1;}
.bew-link{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--blau);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--blau);padding-bottom:2px;}
.bew-link:hover{color:var(--dunkel);border-color:var(--dunkel);}
@media(max-width:900px){
  .bew-karte{flex:0 0 calc(100% - 0px);height:auto;} .bew-arrow{display:none;}
}

/* LEGAL MODALS */
.legal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);z-index:3000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;overflow-y:auto;}
.legal-overlay.open{display:flex;}
.legal-box{background:white;max-width:760px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto;border-radius:8px;padding:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);position:relative;}
.legal-close{position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;background:var(--hell);border:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--dunkel);transition:background 0.2s;}
.legal-close:hover{background:#e0e0e0;}
.legal-box h2{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);font-weight:600;color:var(--dunkel);margin-bottom:28px;padding-right:40px;}
.legal-content h3{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:var(--blau);margin:24px 0 10px;}
.legal-content h3:first-child{margin-top:0;}
.legal-content p{font-size:14px;color:#444;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:12px;}
.legal-content a{color:var(--blau);text-decoration:none;}
.legal-content a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}

/* CAPTCHA */
.captcha-wrap{margin:8px 0;}
.captcha-box{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:white;border:1px solid #d3d3d3;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 16px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;max-width:300px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);transition:border-color 0.2s;}
.captcha-box:hover{border-color:#aaa;}
.captcha-check{width:28px;height:28px;border:2px solid #c1c1c1;border-radius:2px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;background:white;transition:all 0.2s;}
.captcha-box.checked .captcha-check{border-color:#1a73e8;background:#f0f7ff;}
.captcha-spinner{width:16px;height:16px;border:2px solid #e0e0e0;border-top-color:#4285F4;border-radius:50%;animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite;display:none;}
.captcha-tick{display:none;width:18px;height:18px;}
.captcha-box.checking .captcha-spinner{display:block;}
.captcha-box.checked .captcha-tick{display:block;}
.captcha-label{font-size:14px;color:#333;flex:1;padding:0 12px;font-family:sans-serif;}
.captcha-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;}
.captcha-logo-text{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.captcha-logo-text span:first-child{font-size:11px;color:#4285F4;font-weight:bold;font-family:sans-serif;}
.captcha-logo-text span:last-child{font-size:8px;color:#aaa;font-family:sans-serif;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}

.prozess-dots-mobile{display:none;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin:12px 0 20px;}
.prozess-dot-m{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#e0e0e0;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s;}
.prozess-dot-m.aktiv{background:var(--blau);}
@media(max-width:900px){
  .prozess-dots-mobile{display:flex;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- MOBILE MENU -->
<div class="mob-menu" id="mobMenu">
  <button class="mob-close" onclick="toggleMenu()">✕</button>
  <a href="#" onclick="replayHero();toggleMenu()">Startseite</a>
  <a href="#galerie" onclick="toggleMenu()">Galerie</a>
  <a href="#leistungen-wrap" onclick="toggleMenu()">Leistungen</a>
  <a href="#ueber" onclick="toggleMenu()">Über uns</a>
  <a href="#kontakt" onclick="toggleMenu()">Kontakt</a>
</div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo" onclick="replayHero()">
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Schenk Trockenbau" class="logo-img">
      <span class="logo-claim">Moderne Wand- und Deckengestaltung</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#" onclick="replayHero()">Startseite</a>
    <a href="#galerie">Galerie</a>
    <a href="#leistungen-wrap">Leistungen</a>
    <a href="#ueber">Über uns</a>
    <a href="#kontakt">Kontakt</a>
    <a href="#kontakt" class="nav-cta">Anfrage senden</a>
  </div>
  <div class="burger" onclick="toggleMenu()"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-links">
      <div class="hero-tag">Trockenbau Koblenz &amp; Umgebung</div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1">Wände &amp; Decken<br>die <em>begeistern.</em><br>Seit 2011.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Professioneller Trockenbau, Deckengestaltung und Innenausbau – termintreu, fair und mit eigenem Fachpersonal.</p>
      <div class="hero-btn-wrap"><a href="#kontakt" class="hero-btn">Kostenlos anfragen</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-rechts">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Schenk Trockenbau Koblenz">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="ticker-wrap"><div class="ticker">
  <span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Trockenbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Deckengestaltung</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Innenausbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Akustikbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Brandschutz</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Dachausbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Betonoptik</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Koblenz &amp; Umgebung</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Trockenbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Deckengestaltung</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Innenausbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Akustikbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Brandschutz</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Dachausbau</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Betonoptik</span><span class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Koblenz &amp; Umgebung</span>
</div></div>

<!-- GALERIE -->
<section id="galerie">
  <div class="gal-header reveal">
    <h2>Entdecke unsere Projekte.<br><em>Der Schlüssel ist das Detail.</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="ref-liste" id="refListe">
    <div class="ref-empty" id="refEmpty" style="display:none;">Referenzen folgen in Kürze</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LIGHTBOX -->
<div class="lb-overlay" id="lbOverlay" onclick="closeLbIfOutside(event)">
  <div class="lb-box" id="lbBox">
    <div class="lb-foto-wrap">
      <img src="" alt="" class="lb-main-img" id="lbMainImg">
      <div class="lb-vorher-tag" id="lbVorherTag" style="display:none">Vorher / Nachher</div>
      <button class="lb-nav lb-prev" onclick="lbNav(-1)">&#8592;</button>
      <button class="lb-nav lb-next" onclick="lbNav(1)">&#8594;</button>
      <button class="lb-close" onclick="closeLb()">✕</button>
      <div class="lb-thumbs" id="lbThumbs"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="lb-info">
      <div class="lb-kat" id="lbKat"></div>
      <div class="lb-titel" id="lbTitel"></div>
      <div class="lb-text" id="lbText"></div>
      <div class="lb-count" id="lbCount"></div>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="lb-anfrage" onclick="closeLb()">Anfrage zu diesem Projekt →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- LEISTUNGEN -->
<section id="leistungen-wrap">
  <div class="leist-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="sek-tag">Was wir für Sie tun</span>
      <h2 class="sek-titel">Unsere Leistungen</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-grid">
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.0s">
      <div class="leist-nr">01.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Trockenbau</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Trockenbau ist die moderne, wirtschaftliche Bauweise für Wände, Decken und Böden – schnell montiert, sauber verarbeitet und vielseitig einsetzbar. Ob Neubau, Renovierung oder Umbau: Wir planen und montieren Trockenbaukonstruktionen für private und gewerbliche Kunden.</p>
        <ul><li>Schnelle Montage ohne Nassarbeiten</li><li>Für Privat & Gewerbe</li><li>Wände, Decken & Böden</li><li>Termintreue Ausführung</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><rect x="6" y="8" width="36" height="10" rx="1"/><rect x="6" y="22" width="36" height="10" rx="1"/><rect x="6" y="36" width="36" height="6" rx="1"/><line x1="18" y1="8" x2="18" y2="18"/><line x1="30" y1="22" x2="30" y2="32"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.12s">
      <div class="leist-nr">02.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Deckengestaltung</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Abgehängte Decken verbessern nicht nur die Optik eines Raumes – sie sorgen auch für bessere Akustik, verbergen Leitungen und ermöglichen eine effektive Beleuchtungsplanung. Wir realisieren Deckensysteme jeder Art.</p>
        <ul><li>Akustikdecken & Abhängungen</li><li>LED-Beleuchtungsintegration</li><li>Verdeckung von Leitungen</li><li>Design nach Maß</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="6" y1="10" x2="42" y2="10"/><line x1="16" y1="10" x2="16" y2="18"/><line x1="32" y1="10" x2="32" y2="18"/><circle cx="16" cy="22" r="4"/><circle cx="32" cy="22" r="4"/><path d="M8 36 Q24 28 40 36"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.24s">
      <div class="leist-nr">03.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Innenausbau</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Mit Schenk Trockenbau haben Sie einen einzigen Ansprechpartner für Ihren gesamten Innenausbau. Wir übernehmen Trockenbauarbeiten, Bodenbeläge, Malerarbeiten und koordinieren alle notwendigen Gewerke.</p>
        <ul><li>Alles aus einer Hand</li><li>Trockenbau, Böden & Malerarbeiten</li><li>Gewerblich & privat</li><li>Komplette Koordination</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M8 24 L24 10 L40 24"/><rect x="14" y="24" width="20" height="16" rx="1"/><rect x="20" y="30" width="8" height="10"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.36s">
      <div class="leist-nr">04.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Dachausbau</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Ein ausgebauter Dachboden bedeutet mehr Wohnfläche, mehr Wert und mehr Lebensqualität. Wir planen und realisieren den kompletten Dachausbau – inklusive fachgerechter Wärmedämmung nach EnEV, Dampfsperre und sauberer Trockenbaukonstruktion.</p>
        <ul><li>Mehr Wohnfläche gewinnen</li><li>Wärmedämmung nach EnEV</li><li>Dampfsperre & Trockenbau</li><li>Komplettlösung</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 26 L24 8 L42 26"/><rect x="12" y="26" width="24" height="16" rx="1"/><rect x="20" y="16" width="8" height="8" rx="1"/><line x1="24" y1="16" x2="24" y2="24"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.48s">
      <div class="leist-nr">05.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Altbausanierung</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Altbauten haben Charakter – aber oft auch veraltete Substanz. Wir modernisieren Bestandsgebäude mit modernen Trockenbau-Methoden: Innendämmung, neue Trennwände, Deckensanierung und Oberflächenaufbereitung.</p>
        <ul><li>Innendämmung & Wärmeschutz</li><li>Neue Raumaufteilung</li><li>Deckensanierung</li><li>Werterhalt & Aufwertung</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><rect x="8" y="14" width="32" height="26" rx="1"/><path d="M8 14 L24 6 L40 14"/><rect x="16" y="24" width="8" height="16"/><rect x="26" y="20" width="8" height="8" rx="1"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.6s">
      <div class="leist-nr">06.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Brandschutz</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Brandschutz ist keine Option, sondern Pflicht – und erfordert handwerkliche Präzision. Wir errichten zertifizierte Brandschutzwände der Klassen F30 bis F120, Lüftungsschächte L30 bis L90 sowie alle weiteren brandschutztechnischen Konstruktionen.</p>
        <ul><li>F30 bis F120 Brandschutzwände</li><li>Zertifizierte Ausführung</li><li>Lüftungsschächte L30–L90</li><li>Gewerbe & Industrie</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M24 6 L38 12 V26 C38 34 24 42 24 42 C24 42 10 34 10 26 V12 Z"/><path d="M24 18 C24 18 28 22 26 28 C26 28 22 26 22 22 C22 22 20 26 20 28 C18 24 20 18 24 18Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="leist-item  reveal-up" style="transition-delay:0.72s">
      <div class="leist-nr">07.</div>
      <div class="leist-titel">Fugenlose Betonoptik</div>
      <div class="leist-body">
        <p>Als zertifizierter Verarbeiter des Stone Age Systems bieten wir fugenlose Oberflächen in edler Betonoptik an. Die hochwertige Spachtelmasse verbindet sich in nur wenigen Millimetern Aufbauhöhe mit Wänden, Böden und Decken zu einer fugenlosen Einheit.</p>
        <ul><li>Stone Age System zertifiziert</li><li>Wände, Böden & Decken</li><li>Pflegeleicht & langlebig</li><li>Edles Design</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="leist-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><rect x="6" y="6" width="36" height="36" rx="2"/><circle cx="14" cy="16" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="26" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="34" cy="22" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="18" cy="28" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="32" cy="34" r="2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

